{"tid":272163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"癱仔同三哥其實係唔係同一供應商？","createTime":"2017-06-05T15:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T15:43:36.000Z","uid":20836,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3874502cebf6f863584ef9c41294b315cd39c069","tid":272163,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:27:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，本人平時就食開三哥，咁有時口痕附近有冇三哥，咁就會食癱仔，食完之後法國有啲餸係一樣咁，有啲就唔同。好似三哥啲墨丸就實啲，癱仔嘅就發啲。但係雞肉同腐皮就好鬼似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位鍾意三哥或者癱仔嘅巴絲點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7183f5268d93eb76beb61819b04750871197a0be","tid":272163,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"連登唔係好多fans㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己推</span></span>"},{"pid":"8ceebdedef79f0c1a782fba759dfc0173aed71b7","tid":272163,"uid":85306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"三哥難食過屎。<br />\n<br />\n老譚就唔覺好食。<br />\n<br />\n只食過5次老譚。"}]}